I want to be confident in my decisions, and confident in myself moving forward. I want to not be afraid of putting myself out there! I want to not be afraid of trying new things! There's so much I want to do and I hope I'll get to share that will all of you.
I finally have appointments I've been waiting years on, I'm finally in a place I can be more comfortable in, and I'm finally able to start focusing on trying to live instead of just surviving.

In all honestly this past year has been a rough one. It's been a long journey with my personal being and physical/mental health that I'm still grappling to get some semblance of control over, but I cant deny that I've been trying everything within my power to get better.
